title: Intel HD drivers for Windows Server 2008, r2, 2012 and 2012 r2 E

What's working.
HDMI double screen and resolution.  I don't know about the rest.

net 3.5 + desktop experience.

I found some older beta drivers that worked with windows server 2008 r2, then i installed it and i use some program for update the driver (slimdriver) and that's it.

This file contain a virus?.
no, but if you want to be sure then install it in a virtual machine.
